dct_title_s: Plans of Nineveh, Troy, Carthage, Alexandria, and Constantinople
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Title from Contents. At head of map: Dr. William Smith's Ancient atlas. 43. Plate 43 from: Atlas of ancient geography, biblical and classical ... / ... drawn by Dr. Charles Müller ... ; edited by William Smith and George Grove. Historic Maps copy imperfect: top portion of map, showing Nineveh, wanting.
